    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/17cef7b3be87277f9ece053ab6acc32c.poster.avif?t=1667096217\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/17cef7b3be87277f9ece053ab6acc32c.webm?t=1667096217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/17cef7b3be87277f9ece053ab6acc32c.mp4?t=1667096217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>向所有经典的地宫RPG致敬！<br>《龙骑士之墓》是一款地宫角色扮演解谜冒险类游戏。你可以自己建立四人团队，或者由系统提供最优化的团队来进行游戏。游戏提供龙裔，矮人，精灵和人类四个种族，还有战士，法师，牧师，军阀和游侠五个职业可供选择。游戏中还提供技能和天赋，使得每次建立的团队都可以根据自己的抉择而产生不同的特点。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/668b618890dcbfc76b8ea566bc10a57a.avif?t=1667096217\" width=615 height=176 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>空气、火焰、大地、流水、奥术五系法术，魔法师专精，团队的灵魂所在；</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>生命、身体、精神，光明，黑暗五系法术，牧师专精，团队强大的支持；</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>近战、火系、精神魔法和近战技能，军阀专精，可以称得上团队领袖；</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>远程和偷袭技能，游侠专精，团队无可或缺的尖刀；</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>重武器、重甲，永远挡在团队前面的沙包，发狂时的旋风斩，战士专精，经典的团队领袖；</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/5f0522b0dfee4940d23c95a7fc308208.poster.avif?t=1667096217\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/5f0522b0dfee4940d23c95a7fc308208.webm?t=1667096217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/5f0522b0dfee4940d23c95a7fc308208.mp4?t=1667096217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在游戏中，你会遇到各种陷阱机关。阻挡住飞过来的魔法球，以免它触发机关，打开你脚下的致死陷阱。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/13e173116ae6197e557da5569420707f.poster.avif?t=1667096217\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/13e173116ae6197e557da5569420707f.webm?t=1667096217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/13e173116ae6197e557da5569420707f.mp4?t=1667096217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在和怪物战斗之余，你还需要关注你的团队的健康状况。在僻静之处小睡，或者吃点东西以免你的团队成员饿得眼花。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/796bf3d69c5ccb0d17fe911381c12fe4.poster.avif?t=1667096217\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/796bf3d69c5ccb0d17fe911381c12fe4.webm?t=1667096217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/823610/extras/796bf3d69c5ccb0d17fe911381c12fe4.mp4?t=1667096217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>需要补给食物、装备，通过特殊传送门抵达酒馆。和酒馆老板娘深入交谈，喝几杯小歇一下。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>以次时代3D画面，重现上世纪70~90年代的经典电脑游戏；</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>恰如其氛的环境音乐，更适合深夜独自游玩；</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20小时的固定关卡游玩时间，三种难度，多职业和种族的复玩；</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>便捷操作，一个鼠标就可以完成游戏中所有的操作；</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>符文魔法系统，熟记符文的组合，会让你体验到魔法师的感觉；</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>内置地宫编辑器，支持自制关卡；</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
